{"tid":2443980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴口罩凝視警察 售貨員抗拒警務人員罪成判囚3星期","createTime":"2021-03-12T11:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T20:34:43.000Z","uid":56115,"like":10,"dislike":458,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0f47c4f1091945eef327caecc8785c6c915405","tid":2443980,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"前年10月蒙面法生效首日，戴上黑色口罩的售貨員被指在元朗推撞截查他的兩名防暴警，被控一項抗拒警務人員罪，上月被裁定罪成。裁判官<span class=\"red\">王證瑜</span>認為被告的行為有挑戰蒙面法的效果，案情嚴重，但考慮到被告身為家庭經濟之柱，亦擔當患有聽障兄長與父母之間的溝通橋樑，加上犯案後已深感悔意，故酌情減刑，最終判他即時監禁3星期。<br />\n<br />\n惟王官指被告干犯的控罪性質嚴重，判以阻嚇性刑罰、亦即監禁或禁閉式刑罰屬唯一合適選擇。而且本案案情嚴重，被告當時推開警員然後逃走，及至被警員制服時仍不斷掙扎，事件亦導致有警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n王官強調，案發時反修例運動已持續多月，亦是首日實施蒙面法。王官認為被告當日選擇戴上口罩遮蓋臉容，且邊行邊看著警員，舉動是「明顯地故意凝視警員」。"},{"pid":"bbe48c951c68ce30832dc4ae69acd64596f32c58","tid":2443980,"uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":34,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/OAMFNS3ZU5FDLIPV3X7JJGTEDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FOAMFNS3ZU5FDLIPV3X7JJGTEDY%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=9bb7732f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210312%2FOAMFNS3ZU5FDLIPV3X7JJGTEDY%2F&h=abfee0c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210312/OAMFNS3ZU5FDLIPV3X7JJGTEDY/</a>"},{"pid":"ee877ea4d1a57988a5c856489deaab985df48939","tid":2443980,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e93fcfb8d5ba9a957bb6bc88d274fc24de8ace","tid":2443980,"uid":75935,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"眼神攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma