ike":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJSbiVZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJSbiVZ.jpg&h=3bab7d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數碼子走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3275baf9f43390acd0d7f373ab4d26eb7ba14e82","tid":2443980,"uid":104797,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong>香港已經出現「納粹法官」</strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmCCeuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmCCeuw.jpg&h=781f1f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅蘭德&middot;弗萊斯勒 （德語：Roland Freisler，1893年10月30日－1945年2月3日）為一個納粹德國法官。他擔任過希特勒的帝國司法部秘書和人民法院的院長。<br />\n<br />\n人民法院是在憲法授權外成立的機關，主要負責審理關於對抗希特勒獨裁政權的政治活動，並進行過一系列作秀般的公開審訊。<br />\n<br />\n人民法院負責審理各種進行「政治犯罪」的人。這些犯罪被弗萊斯勒主持的法院視為防禦能力的崩潰，並且依此而嚴厲的處刑，許多人甚至因而被判處死刑。<br />\n<br />\n在弗萊斯勒掌管之下，死刑判處率急速上升，進入人民法院審理的人中，最終有將近90%被判處死刑或有期徒刑，且判決通常在審理前就已經決定好了。"},{"pid":"002bfef2e924a7d04372fb4397c2cb5d2705acb1","tid":2443980,"uid":61586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"望咩啊望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6862145142cd5bc41da28d6c7de0fa963217ea","tid":2443980,"uid":41130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d69pDVV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd69pDVV.gif&h=7c733c51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DCzH92G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDCzH92G.gif&h=71b1ab72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UykoUuJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUykoUuJ.gif&h=651d5947&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c97b90016e6f81ea6725d876c634016e77e75e7","tid":2443980,"uid":235796,"like"